OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776564203
OL,3,CStarmer and Macron rally coalition for
OL,4,Cmission to protect the Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FIt's not easy being a European leader
OL,7,Ftrying to play a role on the world
OL,8,Fstage in the time of Trump.
OL,10,FEven as Britain and France were on the
OL,11,Fverge of announcing a multilateral
OL,12,Fmission to reopen the Strait of
OL,13,FHormuz, up pops a Truth Social post
OL,14,Ffrom President Donald Trump announcing
OL,15,Fthe Iranians have agreed to open the
OL,16,FStrait themselves, and anyway, Nato
OL,17,Fand Europe no longer needed and are in
OL,18,Ffact just paper tigers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776564203
OL,3,CStarmer and Macron rally coalition for
OL,4,Cmission to protect the Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FEven so, Keir Starmer and Emmanuel
OL,7,FMacron have made substantial progress
OL,8,Fin Paris today, corralling almost 50
OL,9,Fcountries to discuss the crisis in the
OL,10,FGulf, and getting more than a dozen to
OL,11,Fpromise to contribute 'defensive'
OL,12,Fnaval forces to keep the waterway
OL,13,Fopen, should peace really have broken
OL,14,Fout.
OL,16,FThere were two key points in all this:
OL,17,Fno one else is going to get involved
OL,18,Fin Donald Trump's war, and post-war,
OL,19,Fno American forces are going to be
OL,20,Finvolved in this multinational effort.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776564203
OL,3,CStarmer and Macron rally coalition for
OL,4,Cmission to protect the Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FIf the Americans are unhappy with
OL,7,Fthis, then too bad, but teaming up
OL,8,Fwith the US Navy would risk
OL,9,Fjeopardising the whole effort should
OL,10,Fhostilities break out again.
OL,12,FAs to what this putative force can
OL,13,Fachieve, it seems they will have to be
OL,14,Flimited to mine clearing, intelligence
OL,15,Fand warning of threats.
OL,17,FThe actual escorting of hundreds of
OL,18,Ftankers and other shipping through the
OL,19,FStrait would be way beyond the
OL,20,Fcapacity of any force currently
OL,21,Fenvisaged.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776564203
OL,3,CStarmer and Macron rally coalition for
OL,4,Cmission to protect the Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FThere simply wouldn't be enough ships.
OL,8,FHaving given the political imprimatur
OL,9,Ftoday, there will be a more detailed
OL,10,Fplanning meeting in London next week.
OL,12,FIt may, of course, never happen ` the
OL,13,Fleaders today said the conflict must
OL,14,Fhave ended definitively and there must
OL,15,Fbe no attempt by Iran to levy tolls on
OL,16,Fthe ships they will help pass through,
OL,17,Fand neither of those conditions can be
OL,18,Fmet right now.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776564203
OL,3,CStarmer and Macron rally coalition for
OL,4,Cmission to protect the Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FIndeed, the Iranians are still
OL,7,Finsisting on their right to demand
OL,8,Ftransit fees.
OL,10,FBut it is progress of a sort, and a
OL,11,Fdemonstration that if the US really is
OL,12,Fgoing to withdraw from its role as a
OL,13,Fglobal policeman, there are the
OL,14,Fbeginnings of an effort by European
OL,15,Fleaders to be more assertive globally.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
